{"tid":2442840,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"（好好拍電影）最鍾意許鞍華邊套戲？","createTime":"2021-03-11T15:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T11:12:11.000Z","uid":50216,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ba4e89892c7573a61faa83c5f9bb6a4d0f09cfb9","tid":2442840,"uid":50216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T15:42:34.000Z","msg":"許鞍華拍嘅電影都算多元化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有平淡又溫馨嘅《女人四十》、《桃姐》、《天水圍的日與夜》<br />\n<br />\n緊貼時事嘅《千言萬語》、《天水圍的夜與霧》<br />\n<br />\n靈異題材嘅《瘋劫》、《撞到正》、《幽靈人間》<br />\n<br />\n翻拍張愛玲作品嘅《傾城之戀》、《半生緣》<br />\n<br />\n但宜家睇翻最感觸都係越南三部曲 《越南來客》、《胡越的故事》、《投奔怒海》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qZkTqeT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqZkTqeT.jpg&h=5ebf066d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尤其係投奔怒海<br />\n睇完真係好震撼<br />\n估唔到以前港產片規模可以去到咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77bb95fa0d32060604425cd477990c6a2952d603","tid":2442840,"uid":3567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T15:44:05.000Z","msg":"撞到正想睇返，全部source都係朦查查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9fc5c62c1c678edf1257297b9539df5ba7b356","tid":2442840,"uid":114956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T15:48:14.000Z","msg":"男人四十同姨媽的後現代生活都好睇"},{"pid":"c272f1bf5a2662af3be4004d8d939575b895fe35","tid":2442840,"uid":50216,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"77bb95fa0d32060604425cd477990c6a2952d603","tid":2442840,"uid":3567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T15:44:05.000Z","msg":"撞到正想睇返，全部source都係朦查查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T15:49:00.000Z","msg"